24. Complete Functional Requirement Specification (AI-Ready Prompt Format)



This section ensures that if this document is used as an implementation prompt, no functional layer is omitted.

24.1 Authentication & Authorization Requirements

Authentication:

JWT-based authentication (Access token + Refresh token)

Access token expiry: 15–30 minutes

Refresh token stored securely (HttpOnly cookie)

Logout invalidates refresh token (blacklist or rotation strategy)

Password Rules:

Minimum 8 characters

At least one uppercase, one lowercase, one number

Client-side + server-side validation

Forgot Password Flow:

Request OTP via phone/email

OTP expiry (5 minutes)

Reset password endpoint

Role-Based Access Control:

Middleware validates role before route access

Admin-only routes protected

College-admin scoped access (optional future support)


---

24.2 Complete API Endpoint Map

Auth: POST /api/auth/register POST /api/auth/login POST /api/auth/logout POST /api/auth/refresh POST /api/auth/forgot-password POST /api/auth/reset-password

User: GET /api/users/profile PUT /api/users/profile DELETE /api/users GET /api/users/export

Focus: POST /api/focus/start POST /api/focus/pause POST /api/focus/end GET /api/focus/logs GET /api/focus/stats

Reflections: POST /api/reflections GET /api/reflections

Complaints: POST /api/complaints GET /api/complaints/user GET /api/complaints/:id

Admin Complaints: GET /api/admin/complaints PATCH /api/admin/complaints/:id DELETE /api/admin/complaints/:id

Jobs: GET /api/jobs POST /api/admin/jobs PUT /api/admin/jobs/:id DELETE /api/admin/jobs/:id

Announcements: GET /api/announcements POST /api/admin/announcements PUT /api/admin/announcements/:id DELETE /api/admin/announcements/:id

Analytics: GET /api/admin/analytics GET /api/admin/reports

Weather: GET /api/weather

Community: POST /api/community/posts GET /api/community/posts DELETE /api/community/posts/:id


