24.5 Focus Session Logic Specification

States:

Idle

Running

Paused

Completed

Rules:

Minimum session: 5 minutes

Auto-save every 60 seconds

On tab switch (web), show reminder modal

Post-Session Flow:

Reflection prompt

Mood check

Save to FocusLogs collection

Analytics Computation:

Total weekly minutes

Subject-wise distribution

Streak calculation


---

24.6 Complaint Workflow State Machine

States:

Draft

Submitted

Under Review

Escalated

Resolved

Rejected

Notifications:

On submission

On status change

On resolution

Admin Actions:

Add notes

Change status

Request additional information

Audit Log:

Track every status change

Timestamp + admin ID


---

24.7 Data Privacy & Compliance Requirements

All complaint descriptions encrypted before DB storage

Personally identifiable information minimized

User data export in JSON format

GDPR-style delete confirmation flow

Activity log visible to user


---

24.8 Notification Engine Logic

Types:

Push notifications

In-app banners

Email (optional)

Trigger Examples:

Focus streak about to break

Complaint status update

Job deadline approaching

Severe weather alert

Notification Throttling:

Max 3 per day

Quiet hours (10 PM–6 AM)


